a na ľavej strane tofu s kimchi.
Urobil som aj hviezdu.

382
00:34:00,100 --> 00:34:02,110
<i>"Prepustený z väzenia?"
(Chool-so)</i>

383
00:34:02,110 --> 00:34:04,000
Nie je to tak?

384
00:34:04,000 --> 00:34:07,470
Tak... "Vzhľad"?

385
00:34:08,410 --> 00:34:13,760
